Watering hole attack - it involves third-party system. Attacker hopes that users of your secure network will visit the third-party (watering hole), 
get infected and give attacker a way to network.

Executing the watering hole attack:
    -attaker have to do reserch and determinate which websites the victim group uses.
    -attacker infects one of these  third-party sites. 
    -infected site infects all visitors.

How to prevent?:
    -Defens-in-depth
    -Firewall and IPS
    -Anit-virus/Anti-malware signature updates